{"tid":2300240,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"做個確診中國人 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-11-25T10:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T10:55:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3643216aa9652db7bee454b64d5561b4e77a8d62","tid":2300240,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:55:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201125/YVSVVLPFIZBKTMOOXMCIRUI22U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201125%2FYVSVVLPFIZBKTMOOXMCIRUI22U%2F&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=bd9aa8f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201125%2FYVSVVLPFIZBKTMOOXMCIRUI22U%2F&h=2da4c479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201125/YVSVVLPFIZBKTMOOXMCIRUI22U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n做個確診中國人 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/j5bhMmc93qrvaw_is53yMV3oDfs=/1600x900/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GZ6WIZLHRBGCROC6TWIXFAAVQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fj5bhMmc93qrvaw_is53yMV3oDfs%3D%2F1600x900%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGZ6WIZLHRBGCROC6TWIXFAAVQI.jpg&h=30188947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n昨見網民惡搞《勇敢的中國人》，把其中兩句改為「做個確診中國人 獲派五千感染別人／我為五千蚊 哪懼怕犧牲 終於瓜老襯」，笑到肚痛。我一時技癢，忍不住「冷血」改寫了全首（末兩行則保留網民佳句），抄錄於下，聊博一笑：<br />\n<br />\n「令我穿起舞衣鳩跳 願你通街吐痰傳病／旺角逼爆舞廳 貪佢毒氣騰騰／誓要將那錢賺 鬼咁興奮／（男唱）做個確診中國人 沒有抗爭只有病人／（合唱）我萬眾一心 哪用理醫生 開P開上癮／（女唱）做個確診中國人 莫怕有菌天降財神／（合唱）我為五千蚊 懶下載安心 乞兒都接吻／令我張開個嘴奶柱 願你終於惹埋林鄭／為了普世確診 支爆就靠病人／誓要將這苦難 攻破深圳／（男唱）做個確診中國人 沒有抗爭只有病人／（合唱）咬住隻蝙蝠 糞便也生吞 方艙都照瞓／（女唱）做個確診中國人 獲派五千感染別人／（合唱）我為五千蚊 哪懼怕犧牲 終於瓜老襯」"}]}